# kton binaries are not published here - build them from the plankton repo (see README)
bin/plankton
bin/nekton
bin/kton
# private key material must NEVER be committed to a public repo (belt-and-suspenders: keep this even
# though each example writes its keys under .work/keys/, which we otherwise now PERSIST - see below)
*.key
*.pem
# Each example PERSISTS its .work/ so every foton's recorded input/output path is a real, fetchable
# file in this repo (its raw permalink is the FileRef's carried `uri`). We deliberately do NOT ignore
# .work/ anymore. Only the private signing keys inside it stay ignored (the *.key rule above).
